citation: Youth Participation in Education and Training (Guaranteeing Futures) Act 2005 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Youth Participation in Education and Training (Guaranteeing Futures) Act 2005 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Youth Participation in Education and Training (Guaranteeing Futures) Act 2005 has been repealed by Schedule 6 to the Education Act 2016
